flowchart TD
    A([Query vector]) --> B{Metadata filters present?}
    B -- Yes --> C[Apply pre-filter to narrow candidate set]
    B -- No --> D[Use full index]
    C --> E[ANN index lookup via HNSW or IVF]
    D --> E
    E --> F[Retrieve over-sampled candidate list]
    F --> G{Re-ranking enabled?}
    G -- Yes --> H[Score candidates with exact cosine similarity]
    H --> I[Sort by score, keep top-k]
    G -- No --> I
    I --> J[Fetch text chunks and metadata for top-k IDs]
    J --> K([Return ranked results with scores and payloads])
